Package com.cafean.jobstream.common.components

Class FileType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.jobstream.common.components.FileType
  • public class FileType
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds information indicating a type of file for use by job steps. This is used to insure that only files of the correct type are specified for applications inside a job stream.
